	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />When you're "camera" moves the screen, once you hit the nametable, how will you scroll to the right more? To do that, you must set the main nametable to be the one you're scrolled onto all the way, because to scroll across it more, it has to be the main table since you can't scroll anymore if you set the scroll to the max.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
